text.tspan: Modifications of equipment or substantial changes in short-circuit current available may
void results of the Arc Flash Hazard Analysis Study and values displayed on this Label.
To maintain accuracy, Arc Flash review/update should be performed within 5 years of
latest study/review (CSA Z462 Section 4). For more info contact PowerCore Eng. at
